cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.SOC, cs.CYBER 

The paper deals with fraud activities in mobile app markets, which involves security and privacy concerns (cs.CR). It also involves search algorithms and optimization (cs.IR), user acquisition and retention (cs.SI), and market operations (cs.SOC). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of honeypots to track fraud activities, which falls under the category of cyber deception (cs.CYBER).
